Royal Caribbean, with TravelCard by Inspire, means you can sail away on exciting itineraries to over 250 of the world’s most popular destinations. Royal Caribbean is known for driving innovation at sea, continuously redefining cruise vacationing. Each successive class of ships is an architectural marvel and pushes the envelope of what is possible on a cruise ship. Onboard, the global cruise line has debuted countless industry “firsts” – such as rock climbing, ice skating and surfing at sea – to capture the imagination of families and adventurous vacationers alike